OL,5, Parents said they were furious their   
OL,6, daughters had been taken out of lessons
OL,7, for wearing stretchy black trousers at 
OL,8, a school that recently starred in a BBC
OL,9, documentary about behaviour.           
OL,11,FOne mum claimed some girls had to go   
OL,12,Finto cupboards to change - something   
OL,13,Fthe head of Beacon Hill Academy in     
OL,14,FSedgley denied.                        
OL,16,FThe secondary school said it would buy 
OL,17,Fa uniform if there were "difficulties".
OL,19,FPrincipal Sukhjot Dhami said he made   
OL,20,F"no apologies" of the high standards.  
